<!DOCTYPE styles [
		<!ELEMENT styles (element)+>

		<!ELEMENT element EMPTY>
		<!ATTLIST element name CDATA #REQUIRED
		                style CDATA #REQUIRED
		                foreground CDATA #IMPLIED
		                background CDATA #IMPLIED>
]>
<styles>
  <element name="text" style="plain" foreground="000000"/>
  <element name="key" style="plain" foreground="0000ff"/>
  <element name="comment" style="italic" foreground="808080"/>
  <element name="bracket" style="bold" foreground="2fbf53"/>
  <element name="number" style="plain" foreground="008000"/>
  <element name="error" style="plain" foreground="ff0000"/>
</styles>